| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1960 — Recovery Inhibition (blackbasta)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d7711884-7999-5fcc-bb26-ed1e3ac7a9c4"
